?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182318_5fa90b0b47fb65d6ded903021ce6ed7d.jpg&h=42e0bacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/182421_61a7777026bf6af77e05591f4ec1b27b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182421_61a7777026bf6af77e05591f4ec1b27b.jpg&h=f499451f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/182352_d4b8b555a2531dd3fbcabf543b36673b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182352_d4b8b555a2531dd3fbcabf543b36673b.jpg&h=c9aa481c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係對面花園一見到人就行過黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/182739_4375621aff80f6fdd33c4f2eb4e5ab51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182739_4375621aff80f6fdd33c4f2eb4e5ab51.jpg&h=3aa1aad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢好肥<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/182812_5ce2e81040374ff79b0b16855efbb03a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F182812_5ce2e81040374ff79b0b16855efbb03a.jpg&h=6f32d7ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢真係好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  應該好食好住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183145_15bcde62f0af880132be5bcbe42110b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183145_15bcde62f0af880132be5bcbe42110b0.jpg&h=616f5f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上一秒佢警戒性好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183215_8107760be9cf449f59fdef8c32af94ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183215_8107760be9cf449f59fdef8c32af94ee.jpg&h=5df1adf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下一秒可以變返好chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183641_e529fb112aa0be3ce08ac64728dc6ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183641_e529fb112aa0be3ce08ac64728dc6ae4.jpg&h=020b2765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183715_2afea50a92d3471741743b93bd4fa449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183715_2afea50a92d3471741743b93bd4fa449.jpg&h=6fa3fa48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢真係唔驚人，就咁坐係我地隔離<br />\n同埋佢係咁搵個身磨我地隻腳唔知做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183740_98430993077d1699a1b03791f02c3c79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183740_98430993077d1699a1b03791f02c3c79.jpg&h=3b9e03ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/183804_2f5511666724a7c1cd8aa59fe44fc425.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F183804_2f5511666724a7c1cd8aa59fe44fc425.jpg&h=8ff98fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後送上肉球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0a28bdafe084e04b4ca620b2db0d6e59859028","tid":294833,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後嗰張咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw我係歐洲都成日見到貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> London 超級多 stray cat有陣時你眼望我眼佢就會喵喵叫好似想我去諗撚佢哋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都係，佢地又唔驚人又會主動行埋黎<br />\n你得閒咪同佢地玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60d5930e249b5076a794f98a88c16c1fff0f20c","tid":294833,"uid":5261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"樓豬借d兒貼自拍又要遮住個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d5ceb36a2204598600fa7cd7432e1721beeb05","tid":294833,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PUSSY呢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肉球頂住先啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係粉紅色呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984b2693ecbf46fd6f2560899fc74ba5a1b8cc4f","tid":294833,"uid":39138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬借d兒貼自拍又要遮住個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係想講啲街貓唔同香港個啲<br />\n真係可以同你好close咁貼住影相咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9417f67ec68f9cffdcc36ad75b1638275e0c6d71","tid":294833,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"我認我咸濕誤會左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388f1d65a61d31da620eb78e7b7775134bdfca3e","tid":294833,"uid":68594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T10: